If you want scripts to use the latest ffmpeg version, 
place its compiled files in FFMPEG subfolder, like that - 

ffmpeg.exe
ffplay.exe
ffprobe.exe
avcodec-62.dll
avdevice-62.dll
avfilter-11.dll
avformat-62.dll
avutil-60.dll
swresample-6.dll
swscale-9.dll
 
If there's no FFMPEG files in FFMPEG folder 
then script will try use ones in "UserPlugins" folder 
if they exist there.
